    "There he lived the life of a connoisseur collector, a frequent stop of art cognoscenti.": [],
    "Cooper made use of his personal acquaintance of artists--most notably Picasso and Leger-- to write monographs on contemporary artists.": [],
    "Meanwhile, the importance of his collection began to be clear.": [],
